---
page_title: Text Fields
description: Text fields let users enter and edit text and usually appear in forms. Users may enter text, numbers, or mixed-format types of input.

layout: content
index: true
---

.content
  h1.bx--type-h1 = current_page.data.page_title
  p.bx--type-p.u-pb-2 = current_page.data.description
  p.bx--type-p
    | A label is a short description of the requested input. Labels are not help text, and they donâ€™t provide instruction, but they should be meaningful and clearly indicate what is expected.

  .content-block
    h2.bx--type-h2 Inputs

  .content-block
    h2.bx--type-h4.u-text-blue States
    .row.between-xs.bottom-xs.u-py-5.col-xs-offset-0.col-lg-offset-1
      .col-xs-12.col-md-4.col-lg-3
        h3.bx--type-label.u-uppercase.u-pb-5 Default
        = partial :"components/_text_fields", :locals => { :text => 'Label', :type => 'text', :placeholder => 'Enter name' }
      .col-xs-12.col-md-4.col-lg-3
        h3.bx--type-label.u-uppercase.u-pb-5 Input + Ico
        = partial :"components/_text_fields", :locals => { :text => 'Email', :type => 'email', :placeholder => 'Enter email', :ico => 'mail' }
      .col-xs-12.col-md-4.col-lg-3
        = partial :"components/_text_fields", :locals => { :text => 'Password', :type => 'password', :placeholder => 'Enter password', }

    .row.between-xs.bottom-xs.u-py-5.col-xs-offset-0.col-lg-offset-1
      .col-xs-12.col-md-4.col-lg-3
        h3.bx--type-label.u-uppercase.u-pb-5 Input active
        = partial :"components/_text_fields", :locals => { :text => 'Label', :type => 'text', :placeholder => 'Enter name', :extraclass => 'active' }
      .col-xs-12.col-md-4.col-lg-3
        h3.bx--type-label.u-uppercase.u-pb-5 Input success
        = partial :"components/_text_fields", :locals => { :text => 'Email', :type => 'email', :ico => 'success', :placeholder => 'Enter email', :extraclass => 'active success'  }
      .col-xs-12.col-md-4.col-lg-3
        h3.bx--type-label.u-uppercase.u-pb-5 Input disabled
        = partial :"components/_text_fields", :locals => { :text => 'Password', :type => 'text', :placeholder => 'Enter password', :disabled => true }

    .row.bottom-xs.u-py-5.col-xs-offset-0.col-lg-offset-1
      .col-xs-12.col-md
        h3.bx--type-label.u-uppercase.u-pb-5 Error
        = partial :"components/_text_fields", :locals => { :text => 'Label', :type => 'text', :placeholder => 'Incorrect email, try again', :extraclass => 'error' }

  .clipboard
    h4.bx--type-h4.u-text-blue.uppercase  Code/Html > Save
    .code-wrapper
      .code-content id="input-code"
        = code("html") do
          | <div class="lds-input-field">
              <label class="lds-input-field__label" for="43">Label</label>
              <input name="43" placeholder="Enter name" class="lds-input-field__input" required="required" type="text">
            </div>

      = partial :"components/_code_actions", :locals => { :target => '#input-code'}

  .content-block
    = partial :"blocks/_anatomy", :locals => { :extracolumn => true,  :item => data.component_slider.items.input }

  .content-block
    h1.bx--type-h1 Text Area
    p.bx--type-p.u-pt-4
      | Textarea inputs are used for freeform data entry. They are taller than text fields and wrap overflow text onto a new line. They are a fixed height and scroll vertically when the cursor reaches the bottom of the field. The large initial size indicates that longer responses are possible and encouraged.

  .content-block
    .row.between-xs.top-xs.u-py-7.col-xs-offset-0.col-lg-offset-1
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-5
        .lds-text-field
          label.lds-text-field__label Default
          textarea class="lds-text-field__input" rows="6" cols="50" placeholder="Enter text here.."
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-4
        .lds-text-field
          label.lds-text-field__label  Disabled
          textarea class="lds-text-field__input" rows="6" cols="50" placeholder="Enter text here.." disabled="disabled"

    .row.between-xs.top-xs.u-pt-5.u-pb-9.col-xs-offset-0.col-lg-offset-1
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-4
        .lds-text-field
          label.lds-text-field__label  Active
          textarea class="lds-text-field__input" rows="6" cols="50" class="active" placeholder="Enter text here.."
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-4
        .lds-text-field
          label.lds-text-field__label  Error
          textarea class="lds-text-field__input" rows="6" cols="50" class="error" placeholder="Enter text here.."
          span.error.message Validation message here

  .clipboard
    h4.bx--type-h4.u-text-blue.uppercase  Code/Html > Save
    .code-wrapper
      .code-content id="textarea"
        = code("html") do
          | <div class="lds-text-field">
              <label class="lds-text-field__label">Default</label>
              <textarea class="lds-text-field__input" cols="50" placeholder="Enter text here.." rows="6"></textarea>
            </div>

      = partial :"components/_code_actions", :locals => { :target => '#textarea' }

  .content-block.text-field__anatomy
    .row.between-xs.top-xs.u-py-7.col-xs-offset-0.col-lg-offset-1
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-5.col-lg-4
        h3.bx--type-label.u-pb-5.u-uppercase Measures
        = image_tag 'uicomponents/inputs/textarea_measures.png', class: 'image-2x';
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-5.col-lg-4
        h3.bx--type-label.u-pb-5.u-uppercase Specifications
        = image_tag 'uicomponents/inputs/textarea_specs.png', class: 'image-2x';
    .row.between-xs.top-xs.u-py-7.col-xs-offset-0.col-lg-offset-1
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-5.col-lg-4
        h3.bx--type-label.u-pb-5.u-uppercase Spacing
        = image_tag 'uicomponents/inputs/textarea_spacing.png', class: 'image-2x';
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-5.col-lg-4
        h3.bx--type-label.u-pb-5.u-uppercase Padding
        = image_tag 'uicomponents/inputs/textarea_padding.png', class: 'image-2x';

  .footer-navigation
    .footer-navigation__previous
      = previous_link(data.title['uielements'])
    .footer-navigation__next
      = next_link(data.title['uielements'])

